{
  "stem": "10862.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Again, the sanitation, the hunger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The morale had already at that time was already beginning to get very, very bad because people-- it was already dragging out for four years.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't seem like the end is ever going to come, and people were already giving up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of people actually gave up, and the ones that gave up so easily died too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They just said, what's the sense in living?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's no-- there's no sense in living anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Reva, how much time did you spend in Czestochowa being afraid?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Czestochowa?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the whole year while I was there, because even though I worked in the factory my life still was very much in danger because I still was a little girl, tried to pretend that I was an adult, tried to pretend that I could work, you know?",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my life was in danger every moment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, any German could have just shot me, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing would have prevented him to kill me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I guess-- you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've always had a belief that my destiny was to survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I honestly feel that there was a reason for me to survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when you walk around and you're afraid of--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Living in fear?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you never know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're always constantly looking over your shoulder because you never know is this going to be your last moment?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Are you going to die tomorrow?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, you're just never, never know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're a constantly fear that maybe any word I say or anything, any action that I do, this soldier might kill me, because they had absolutely no-- what is the word?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They, themselves, there was no morality there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, this man, this soldier-- the one that shot the 11 children-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
